## Email Delivery

The script uses the local Postfix relay via `/usr/sbin/sendmail` — no SMTP
credentials required. Postfix on the bastion is configured with
`inet_interfaces = loopback-only` and relays through the internal mail infrastructure.

The `.xlsx` file is attached to the email. Delivery may take a few minutes depending
on the internal relay.

