## Troubleshooting

|Symptom                    |Fix                                                                                                                                                                   |
|---------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|`No module named openpyxl` |`python3 -m pip install openpyxl --user`                                                                                                                              |
|All nodes show `shared/n/a`|Check node labels: `oc get node <name> -o json | python3 -c "import json,sys; [print(k,'=',v) for k,v in sorted(json.load(sys.stdin)['metadata']['labels'].items())]"`|
|Memory shows decimals      |MachineSet lookup failed — check RBAC: `oc get machinesets -n openshift-machine-api`                                                                                  |
|Email not received         |Check mail queue: `mailq` and logs: `sudo tail -50 /var/log/maillog`                                                                                                  |
|Cluster name shows full ID |Auto-strip of 5-char suffix failed — use `--cluster-name ocpuat` override                                                                                             |
|`oc` command fails         |Verify login: `oc whoami`                                                                                                                                             |